---
title: Lentil-Veggie Mulligatawny with Cilantro and Basmati Rice
description: This Mulligatawny is a traditional curry stew with origins in Indian cuisine that checks all the boxes of being comforting, cozy and filling. Mildly spicy, creamy, loaded with lentils and spinach it's simply delicious!
